## Suggested team allocation (4 people)

- **Backend / orchestration lead:** Phases 1, 2, 4. Owns the blackboard, the agent runtime, the SSE pipeline.
- **Frontend lead:** Phases 1 (frontend portion), 5. Owns the agent panels, layout, polish.
- **Multimodal / tools lead:** Phase 3. Owns PDF parsing, image vision, web research, demo asset preparation.
- **Demo / deployment / glue:** Phases 0, 6. Owns Vultr, deployment scripts, README, demo video, rehearsal coaching, plus floating support across all phases.

Two-person team: combine backend+multimodal and frontend+demo. Cut Phase 3's URL paste and one of the polish items in Phase 5.

